@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<section class="about-hero">
    <p class="about-tag">About The Project</p>
    <h1>Student Budget Tracking System</h1>
    <p class="about-intro">
        The Student Budget Tracking System is a web-based capstone project developed to help students
        manage their personal finances more effectively. It provides a simple platform where users can
        record allowance, monitor expenses, and review their financial status through organized records
        and visual summaries.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-card">
        <h2>What The System Does</h2>
        <p>
            The system allows students to add budget entries, categorize their expenses, view their
            transaction history, and monitor their remaining balance. It also includes dashboard summaries
            and chart-based reports to make spending patterns easier to understand.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
        <h2>Why It Matters</h2>
        <p>
            Many students struggle with budgeting their daily allowance. This project was created to
            encourage financial awareness, discipline, and better decision-making by giving students
            a clear and user-friendly budgeting tool.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
        <h2>Project Goal</h2>
        <p>
            The main goal of this project is to provide an accessible budgeting system that supports
            students in developing responsible money management habits while making expense tracking
            easier, faster, and more organized.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
